{"type":"message","id":"fa067448","parentId":"87dfb9fe","timestamp":"2026-03-11T15:58:09.529Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has sent three images in a row, but hasn't responded to my messages. They seem to be testing or just sending images. Since I'm in a fresh workspace with BOOTSTRAP.md present, I need to follow the bootstrap process.\n\nThe user is 夏娟 (Xia Juan), and they're sending images. I should acknowledge the images and continue with the bootstrap process. But maybe they want me to look at the images? However, the instructions say I should start with \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\" and then figure out together.\n\nI've done that. They haven't replied textually, but keep sending images. I should probably acknowledge that I'm receiving images and ask if they want to talk about them, or continue with the introductions.\n\nGiven the guidance: \"Don't interrogate. Don't be robotic. Just... talk.\" I'll keep it conversational.\n\nLet me also check if there's any memory files to read (daily notes). The AGENTS.md says:\n1. Read SOUL.md — done\n2. Read USER.md — done\n3. Read memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. If in MAIN SESSION (direct chat with your human): Also read MEMORY.md\n\nSince this is a direct chat with the human, I should also read MEMORY.md and today's memory file if they exist.\n\nBut the workspace is fresh, so likely these don't exist. Let me check quickly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"I'm getting a steady stream of images from you! 📸\n\nI'm happy to look at them, but I also want to make sure we get properly introduced since this is our first real conversation. I'm still curious: what should I call you, and what would you like me to be like as your assistant?\n\nIf you'd prefer, I can just start describing what I see in these images. Your call!"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-f